Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:33.20,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,657)}{\fad(500,0)}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:37.29,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to act tough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.09,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scribbling someone made...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:49.88,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,On the wall, of a flower is swaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:55.47,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:57.77,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we both lose and gain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.19,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,By embarking on this long, long path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:08.86,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}And though there may be days loneliness strikes and makes us weep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.37,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's transform our tears and pains to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:22.37,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's light a candle to illuminate our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:27.51,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll hold our small hands over the fire to create stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:32.72,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,And an eternity that shines so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:38.10,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewells may be unavoidable,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:44.02,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yet the seasons continue to change obliviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:48.11,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose myself, I'll continue to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:52.15,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:56.41,ED02 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}That's the only thing I'd like to never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:37.29,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,強がらなくていいんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.09,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが描いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:49.88,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,壁の落書きの花が　揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:55.47,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,自分らしさなんて, 誰もわからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:57.77,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,長い長い道の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.19,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,失くしたり, 拾ったり,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:08.86,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}急に寂しくなって, 泣いちゃう日もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.37,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}涙も　痛みも　星に変えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:22.37,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}明日を照らす　灯りをともそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:27.51,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さな手かざして　ふたりで作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:32.72,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,星屑を　強く光る永遠を探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:38.10,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,さよなら　いつかは来るかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:44.02,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}季節はそれでも巡り巡ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:48.11,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,小さく迷っても　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:52.15,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,君と歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:56.41,ED02 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,950)}それだけは変わらないでいようね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:37.29,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogaranakute iindane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.09,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka ga kaitetta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:49.88,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabe no rakugaki no hana ga yureru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:55.47,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibunrashisa nante dermo wakaranaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:57.77,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagai nagai michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.19,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakushitari hirottari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:08.86,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kyuu ni samishikunatte naichau hi mo arukedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:16.37,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Namida mo itami mo hoshi ni kaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:22.37,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ashita wo terasu akari wo tomosou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:27.51,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisana te kazashite futari de tsukurou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:32.72,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshikuzu wo tsuyoku hikaru eien wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:38.10,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayonara itsuka wa kurukamoshirenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:44.02,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Kisetsu wa soredemo meguri megutteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:48.11,ED02 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiisaku mayottemo aruiteku
