Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.08,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:53.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please... kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.82,Default-alt,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.17,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just staring out into space for, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.13,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hesitating?!
